## Limitations

The findings are based on publicly available information and may not cover all aspects of practical research. The sources used are primarily from online forums and educational websites, which may not provide the depth of peer-reviewed academic research. Additionally, the interpretation of what constitutes "practical" and "realistic" can vary across different fields and contexts.